      <title>Leading Balkan Cartel member arrested in Montenegro</title>
      <link>https://www.europol.europa.eu/media-press/newsroom/news/leading-balkan-cartel-member-arrested-in-montenegro</link>
      <description>On 15 April 2026, Europol supported law enforcement authorities in Montenegro in conducting a large-scale operation targeting a significant cell of the Balkan Cartel. Europol also supported law enforcement authorities in Germany regarding the investigation targeting potential contact persons. This action day resulted in the arrest of twelve suspects (four in Germany), including a High Value Target (HVT) apprehended in Montenegro.</description>
